=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n華拉堤後場短傳組織係幾靚既 好多都到隊友腳<br />\n不過係巴黎 尼馬包皮會退後到中場攞波 左右閘又成日標前 拉比奧特/另一中場又向前進一兩格上去 佢都唔洗點長傳咁濟 <br />\n依家佢主要係中圈-禁區頂防守 偏偏佢落剷又狼死 下下唔識收 <br />\n整體黎講一定唔到派路級數架啦"},{"pid":"7836f7a9d3d37866055909f40cb95ef8a0ab3e9c","tid":460583,"uid":75440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"siuma"},{"pid":"4018f96e287a3bbe006996ae7fb028b12e473967","tid":460583,"uid":3028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:04:42.000Z","msg":"森多利亞個torreira"},{"pid":"25b1ec5b214452fbe2b1f241a120cfc50a9cb5fb","tid":460583,"uid":3028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:05:23.000Z","msg":"napoli個jorginho"},{"pid":"f5c85898f4841232a6bca2b2e01276d4e19fb47b","tid":460583,"uid":46527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"De Bruyne"},{"pid":"38147bb516051327921f83003750955fc68f2cc4","tid":460583,"uid":26959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"近兩三季既YAYA"},{"pid":"8b116b971facd65f4b1b348030dbaa09d085f46d","tid":460583,"uid":26959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>De Bruyne</blockquote><br />\n而家係BOX TO BOX黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c9bc01df217c0e402b0dc85d9b00b0b6b2fb40","tid":460583,"uid":60206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T01:43:45.000Z","msg":"名都有得你叫...<br />\n<br />\n祖派路"},{"pid":"00a6e006fbd996928c81b56076933f576a937cd6","tid":460583,"uid":8775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3563c15692ee68969da1b5d6f2f3571bb2981d95","tid":460583,"uid":19556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒙度利禾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"